org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.predicates

  • Packages that use org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.predicates 
    Package Description
    org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core
    Provides provides core classes used just internally by CloudSim Plus, except the CloudSim class that is the start point and main class used to run simulations.
    org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.predicates  
  • Classes in org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.predicates used by org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core 
    Class and Description
    Predicate
    Predicates are used to select events from the deferred queue, according to required criteria.
    PredicateAny
    A predicate which will match any event on the deferred event queue.
    PredicateNone
    A predicate which will not match any event on the deferred event queue.
